1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,089
At the entrance to the Underground Temple... a figure waits.

2
00:00:05,089 --> 00:00:06,932
He is not a guardian.

3
00:00:06,932 --> 00:00:08,336
Not an explorer.

4
00:00:08,336 --> 00:00:14,566
Just a man who has made himself comfortable at the edge of catastrophe.

5
00:00:14,566 --> 00:00:25,886
The Suspicious Man offers information in exchange for Balrog Skin — trading on the very danger that others are trying to contain.

6
00:00:25,886 --> 00:00:36,854
Whether he knows more than he lets on... or simply profits from proximity to disaster... is a question no one has time to answer.
